--- FIX: VCC-007 [CRITICAL] Supabase tables without Row Level Security
+++ Location: volunteers, donations, sites tables — RLS disabled

# Enable Row Level Security on all tables

```sql
-- Enable RLS
ALTER TABLE volunteers ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
ALTER TABLE donations ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
ALTER TABLE sites ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;

-- Create policies (example: users can only read their own data)
CREATE POLICY "Users read own data" ON volunteers
  FOR SELECT USING (auth.uid() = user_id);

CREATE POLICY "Admins full access" ON volunteers
  FOR ALL USING (auth.jwt() ->> 'role' = 'admin');
```

